"{\"uid\": \"punchng.com-breaking-botswana-declares-holiday-to-honour-olympics-gold-medalist-letsile-tebogo\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Most Widely Read Newspaper  Letsile Tebogo  Kindly share this story:  Botswana's President, Mokgweetsi Masisi, has declared an afternoon day-off today, August 9, 2024, to honour Letsile Tebogo, the country's first-ever Olympics Gold medalist in the 200m.This recognition celebrates Tebogo's achievement as both the first Motswana and the first African to secure gold in this event.The President's proclamation reflects the nation's respect for Tebogo's success and is a tribute to his late mother, marking this occasion in Botswana's sporting history.A Friday statement from the president's X account issued by his Permanent Secretary disclosed this.The press release was from the office of the president, Republic of Botswana, Gaborone.It read, \\\"His Excellency, Dr. Mokgweetsi Eric Keabetswe Masisi, President of the Republic of Botswana, has announced an afternoon day-off for all Batswana and residents today, Friday, August 9, 2024, to honour Letsile Tebogo.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 70, \"end\": 78, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6976268213279153e-19, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mokgweetsi Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\"}, {\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.643816374629673e-19, \"text\": \"Motswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi